characterCustomizations.biography:
I main Balance, and can play resto as OS for raids, I keep MS up to date with Azerite sets for Fortified, Tyrannical and Raid setups, as well as a raid equipped Resto spec generally within 5-7 ilvl of DPS set.

Being mostly an M+ player, I like to run on discord and co-ordinate CD usage correctly to maximise dungeon clear efficiency.

​

For reference I was at the following rankings over the different seasons as different faction/server.

8.0 - 1250 Balance / Alt 1265 Brewmaster

7.3.5 3300IO in 7.3.5 as Boomy/Resto/Guardian | Alt Warlock at 1700 (barely played)

​

I have raided over 10 years as Tank Healer and DPS on a multitude of specs (basically everything except DPS warrior/rogue/dh), I am pretty versatile and generally play to at least an 80th percentile on most characters if effort is given to the character (2-3 Specs at a time)

​
